name: American Airlines MD-82 [N467AA] Close Up Taxi and Takeoff from Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
On American's Dallas-Calgary route, they've switched to using the MD-80 once again, nice to see these classic aircraft back here this winter.  Probably the last year they'll be around. Enjoy this 28 year old mad dog taxiing close up and rocketing off into the crisp winter sky!

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
